    "roster_panel_header": "kilas Roster Key tye mamegi differentiation command center. Create latin kwan dul ki unique learning profiles (grade level, leb, reading level, interests, DOK), then apply those profiles i any generator. Roster matter tye stored i mamegi browser's local storage ki never leaves mamegi device unless in explicitly export onyo sync i matye ka ngolo session. Tii 'Tic ki i Generator' i instantly configure settings pi dul, onyo 'Differentiate by dul' i batch-generate resources pi ducu dul at once.",
    "roster_import_export": "Import previously exported roster JSON buk, onyo export mamegi current roster pi backup onyo sharing kin devices. Exported buk contain dul nying, colors, latin kwan assignments, ki ducu profile settings.",
    "roster_sync_session": "Push mamegi roster dul metadata i active Firebase session so latin kwan tye automatically assigned i their designated dul ka they join. dul-mukene settings (TTS speed, karaoke mode) take effect wi latin kwan devices.",
    "roster_batch_generate": "Generate differentiated resources pi every dul simultaneously. Yer which resource types i create (adapted text, glossary, quiz, etc.) ki system will iterate ki bot lwak dul, applying their profile settings before generating. Resources tye tagged ki dul identifiers pi mayot filtering.",
    "bridge_send_button": "Yab Bridge Mode i cwal bilingual messages i latin kwan during matye ka ngolo instruction. Type tam, lok madwong, onyo instructions, yer mode (Explain, Translate, onyo Visual+Explain), ki yer kit dul. message tye yene using AI ki dul's leb ki reading level settings, then displayed as large, readable bilingual gicaa wi latin kwan devices ki TTS ki karaoke highlighting.",
