      "the_earliest_fraction_notation_dates_t": "Lanyut me bute mukwongo obeddo ki i Ejipt macon macalo mwaka 1800 BCE. Jo Ejipt gutiyo ki \"bute me unit\" — bute ma namba malo obeddo 1 keken (macalo 1/2, 1/3, 1/4). Gucoyo bute mo keken macalo cokke me bute me unit: 2/5 = 1/3 + 1/15. Lanyut me bar me kombeddi (namba malo i wi namba piny) a ki i lu-matematik me Arab me dyere macalo mwaka 1200 CE.",
      "where_do_the_fraction_words_come_from": "Nyig lok me bute a ki kwene?",
      "numerator_comes_from_the_latin_numerar": "\"Numerator\" a ki i Latin \"numerare\" (kwano) — kwano bute adi. \"Denominator\" a ki i \"denominare\" (cako nying) — cako dit me bute. Kacel: namba piny cako kit me bute; namba malo kwano bute adi me meno ma itye kwede.",
      "the_decimal_point": "Cukcuk me decimal",
      "decimals_as_we_know_them_were_populari": "Decimal kit ma wangeyo kwede Simon Stevin oketo gucaŋŋe i 1585 i buk mere \"De Thiende\" (Me Apar). Ma peya meno, bute keken obeddo yo me nyuto namba ma pe pong. Cukcuk me decimal odoko me lobo weng i mwaka 1700 keken.",
      "what_does_percent_mean": "I cent te lok ango?",
      "percent_comes_from_the_latin_per_centu": "\"Percent\" a ki i Latin \"per centum\" — \"i mia acel.\" Pi meno 25% te lok 25 i 100, onyo 25/100. Lanyut me % oa ki i cukcuk me \"per c.\" i coc me cato wil me Italy me mwaka 100 me apar wiye abic.",
      "what_is_a_reciprocal": "Reciprocal en ango?",
      "the_reciprocal_of_a_b_is_b_a_flip_it_u": "Reciprocal me a/b obeddo b/a — lokke malo-piny. Bute mo keken ma pe zero tye ki reciprocal. Anyim me bute ki reciprocal mere obeddo 1 kare ducu: (3/4) × (4/3) = 12/12 = 1. Man obeddo mumiyo poko ki bute rom ki anyim ki reciprocal mere.",
      "why_is_1_2_the_most_used_fraction": "Piŋo 1/2 obeddo bute ma gitiyo kwede loyo?",
      "1_2_is_the_most_common_fraction_in_eve": "1/2 obeddo bute ma nen loyo i lok me nino ki nino pien tye i dyere atir me 0 ki 1. Bene obeddo bute keken ma waco ki lok: \"nucu\" pe \"acel i wi aryo.\" Leb mukene bene tye ki nyig lok mapat pi 1/3 ki 1/4 (bute adek, bute angwen).",
      "pizza_is_mathematical": "Pizza obeddo me matematik",
      "a_pizza_is_a_perfect_fraction_model_be": "Pizza obeddo model me bute atir pien obeddo cil (pi meno bute weng a ki i cwiny), bute yot me kwano, ki model rwatte ki tir me matematik: bute n/d obeddo n bute marom i kin bute weng d marom.",
      "when_fractions_are_not_enough": "Ka ma bute pe romo",
      "some_numbers_like_and_2_cannot_be_writ": "Namba mogo, macalo π ki √2, pe twero coyo macalo bute me namba aryo mupong. Man gilwoŋo namba ma pe tye ki tir. Jo Pythagoras (macalo 500 BCE) giwaco ni gineko lu-matematik Hippasus i kare ma onyuto ni √2 pe twero coyo macalo bute.",
      "continued_fractions": "Bute ma medde",
      "any_real_number_can_be_written_as_a_co": "Namba ada mo keken twero coyo macalo \"bute ma medde\" — bute ma tye iye macalo 1 + 1/(2 + 1/(2 + 1/(2 + ...))). Man miyo pim me bute maber loyo. π ≈ 22/7 ki i nyig lok manok mukwongo; maber loyo obeddo 355/113.",
      "fractions_in_music": "Bute i wer",
      "musical_pitch_ratios_are_fractions_the": "Pim me dwaan me wer obeddo bute. Octave obeddo pim me 2:1 (frequency medde tyen aryo). Me abic atir obeddo 3:2. Me adek madit obeddo 5:4. Pythagoras onongo ni pim me namba mupong ma yot cweyo dwaan ma rwatte.",
      "why_the_common_denominator": "Piŋo namba piny marom?",
      "two_pizzas_can_only_be_combined_if_the": "Pizza aryo twero riyo keken ka ngolo i bute me dit acel-lu. Namba piny mapatpat = bute me dit mapatpat = pe twero riyo atir. Namba piny marom te lok atir \"bute me dit acel-lu.\"",
      "baseball_stats_are_fractions": "Statistik me baseball obeddo bute",
      "a_batting_average_like_333_means_1_3_o": "Average me goyo macalo .333 te lok 1/3 me goyo miyo goyo. ERA me lacwal, percent me bedo-i-base, percent me goyo — weng obeddo bute. Baseball obeddo tuk mukwongo ma ocaŋo kit me tam me statistik man, cakke i mwaka 1850.",
      "cuisenaire_rods": "Odoo pa Cuisenaire",
      "georges_cuisenaire_was_a_belgian_prima": "Georges Cuisenaire obeddo lapwony me primary me Belgium i mwaka 1950 ma ocweyo odoo ma tye ki rangi ki bor 1 nio 10 me konyo lutino mako kube me namba kacel ki bute. \"Kor ot me bute\" ma ineno i klas mapol obeddo latin me dijital me odoo mere ma tye ada.",
      "fractions_in_ancient_china": "Bute i Cayina macon",
      "the_chinese_mathematical_text_nine_cha": "Coc me matematik me Cayina \"Dul Ojiŋ i wi Lonyo me Matematik\" (macalo 100 BCE) onongo tye ki kwano me bute, kacel ki yoo me yenyo namba piny marom ma rwatte i matematik ki ngo ma wapwonyo tin.",
      "computers_and_fractions": "Kombiwuta ki bute",
      "computers_store_decimal_fractions_in_b": "Kombiwuta gikano bute me decimal i binary. Decimal 0.1 pe twero nyuto atir i binary — odoko bute ma dwogo i base 2. Man mumiyo 0.1 + 0.2 miyo 0.30000000000000004 kare mogo i leb me programming.",
      "fraction_adjacent_sayings": "🗣 Carolok ma kube ki bute",
      "dogs_spend_about_1_2_their_lives_sleep": "Guk tiyo macalo 1/2 me kwo gi ki nino. Guk me mwaka 12 onino macalo mwaka 6.",
      "cats_sleep_about_2_3_of_every_day_that": "Pusi nino macalo 2/3 me nino ki nino. Meno obeddo cawa 16 i nino.",
      "elephants_drink_about_1_8_of_their_bod": "Lyec mato macalo 1/8 me pek me kom gi me pii i nino. Lyec me pound 12,000 mato pii me pound 1,500!",
      "a_blue_whale_s_tongue_weighs_about_1_2": "Leb me whale marac-lwak pek macalo 1/2 me motoka matidi (~pound 6,000).",
      "a_bee_visits_about_1_500_flowers_to_ma": "Kic limo macalo turo 1,500 me timo 1/12 me spoon me mo kic.",
      "a_giraffe_s_neck_is_about_1_3_of_its_t": "Ŋut me twiga obeddo macalo 1/3 me bor mere weng.",
      "a_snail_moves_at_about_1_40_of_a_mile_": "Kudu wot macalo 1/40 me mile i cawa. Bikwanyo cawa 40 me mol mile 1.",
      "a_kangaroo_can_leap_a_distance_about_3": "Kangaroo twero cato bor macalo 3/2 me bor me kom mere i cato acel.",
      "a_dolphin_sleeps_with_half_its_brain_a": "Dolphin nino ki nucu me wic mere i kare acel — 1/2 me wic keken yweyo ka ma nucu mukene obeddo makwo.",
      "a_giant_tortoise_can_live_to_150_years": "Kut madit twero kwo nio mwaka 150+. Kut me mwaka 100 okwo 2/3 me kwo mere ma twero.",
      "animal_fractions": "🐾 Bute me lee",
      "real_world_fraction_facts_from_the_ani": "Ada me bute me lobo ada ki i ker me lee. Tii macalo lapeny me coc, gin me mako par, onyo kube-cross me science.",
