      "barry_harris_1929_2021_codified_bebop_": "Barry Harris (1929-2021) oketo cik pa harmony me bebop. Kit tic mere tiyo ki 6th chords ka ma tiyo ki 7ths dok medo diminished passing chords i kin degree pa scale wek dwon owot maber.",
      "ii_v_i_jazz": "ii-V-I (Jazz)",
