      "attack_time_to_reach_full_volume_decay": "Attack: cawa me o i volume ma opong. Decay: cawa me lorre i sustain. Sustain: level pa volume ma imako. Release: cawa me too woko ka iweko key.",
      "a_scale_is_an_ordered_set_of_pitches_m": "Scale obedo cok pa pitches ma oyubu maber. Modes gin lokke pa scale ma cakke ki i degree mapatpat. Ngom acel acel yubo tam mapatpat.",
      "chords_are_built_by_stacking_intervals": "Kigero chords ki gruko intervals (3rds). Major tiyo ki major 3rd + minor 3rd. Minor lokogi. Extended chords medo 7ths, 9ths, ki mukene.",
      "kicks_use_a_sine_oscillator_with_a_pit": "Kicks tiyo ki sine oscillator ma tye ki pitch sweep. Snares riibo koko (ma otwodo) + tone body. Hi-hats tiyo ki high-pass filtered noise bursts.",
      "4_4_4_quarter_note_beats_per_bar_most_": "4/4 = quarter-note beats 4 i bar acel (ma nen dwong). 3/4 = winyo me waltz. 6/8 = compound duple. 5/4 ki 7/8 yubo grooves ma pe rom, me lobo mukene.",
      "keys_arranged_by_ascending_5ths_clockw": "Kiyubo keys ki 5ths ma daño malo lubo cawa. Keys ma cok i kingi poko note 6 ki i 7. Cito lubo cawa medo sharps; ka pe lubo cawa medo flats.",
      "every_musical_sound_contains_overtones": "Dwon pa wer weng tye ki overtones malo pa fundamental. Teko gi ma poro yubo timbre — mano aye mumiyo trumpet winnye mapat ki flute i pitch acel.",
      "an_interval_is_the_distance_between_tw": "Interval obedo bor ma tye i kin pitches aryo, ki pimo i semitones. Frequency ratio yubo consonance (ratios mayot calo 3:2 winnye maber).",
      "plays_chord_notes_one_at_a_time_in_seq": "Goyo notes pa chord acel acel i yoo. Malo = ki piny cito malo, Piny = ki malo cito piny. Yubo patterns ma mol ki i chords ma pe wot.",
      "a_filter_removes_frequencies_above_low": "Filter kwanyo frequencies ma tye malo (lowpass), piny (highpass), onyo i alwora (bandpass) pa cutoff frequency. Resonance (Q) medo frequencies ma cok ki cutoff, yubo peak.",
      "tremolo_periodic_volume_changes_amplit": "Tremolo: alokaloka pa volume i cawa (amplitude modulation). Vibrato: alokaloka pa pitch i cawa (frequency modulation). Weng aryo kigwoko ki LFO (Low Frequency Oscillator).",
      "discovered_in_1983_a_noise_burst_feeds": "Kinongo i 1983. Noise burst donyo i delay line macek adada ma tye ki feedback. Delay time yubo pitch. Filter i feedback loop gwoko ryeny ki decay. Lubo plucked strings i yoo me kwena.",
      "the_sequencer_is_a_composition_tool_ea": "Sequencer obedo jami me yubo wer. Step acel acel cung pi subdivision pa beat. Row pa melody keto pitched notes, drums medo rythm. Musical notation nyuto gin ma iyubo.",
      "notes_on_lines_and_spaces_represent_pi": "Notes ma tye i lines ki spaces cung pi pitches. Kinyuto rumo ki kit pa note: whole (○), half (𝅗𝅥), quarter (♩), eighth (♪). Staff tye ki lines 5.",
