      "equal_temperament_12_notes_per_octave_": "Equal temperament: notes 12 i octave, ratio 2^(1/12). A4 = 440 Hz; A5 = 880 Hz. Well-Tempered Clavier pa Bach (1722) oyubo lobo me ye lok man. Note acel acel ma igoyo kany tye i grid meno.",
