      "pluto_is_still_in_the_solar_system_it_": "Pluto pud tye i solar system! Gilokko nyiŋe ki i \"planet\" odoko \"dwarf planet\" i 2006, ento pud wiro i kom Ceŋ.",
      "the_asteroid_belt_is_mostly_empty_spac": "Kor asteroid dwoŋ mere obedo ka nono! Bor ma tye i kin asteroid obedo milion km. Yeya me polo kato iye labongo peko mo.",
      "not_always_saturn_is_95x_earth_s_mass_": "Pe kare ducu! Saturn pek mere tyen 95 loyo Lobo ento gravity i wi ngom obedo 1.06g keken pien dit twatwal dok pek mere nok. Pek nyo pek pa dano jenge i pek KI bor pa dyere.",
      "all_parts_of_the_moon_receive_sunlight": "Kabedo pa Dwe ducu nongo ryeny me ceŋ! \"Tuŋ ma cen\" obedo nucce ma wan pe watwero neno ki i Lobo pi tidal locking. Nongo ceŋ marom.",
      "the_habitable_zone": "Kabedo me Kwo",
      "the_habitable_zone_or_goldilocks_zone_": "Kabedo me kwo (onyo \"Goldilocks zone\") obedo bor ma ki i lakalatwe ka ma pii twero mol iye i wi ngom pa planet. I solar system megwa, Venus tye i aguu ma iye, Lobo tye i dyere, dok Mars tye i aguu ma woko. Ento me bedo ki pii ma mol imito bene yamo maber ki teko me magnet!",
      "the_greenhouse_effect": "Greenhouse Effect",
      "when_sunlight_heats_a_planet_s_surface": "Ka ryeny me ceŋ tuko wi ngom pa planet, wi ngom cwalo lyeto (infrared) woko. Gas me greenhouse (CO₂, CH₄, H₂O) mwonyo lyeto man ci dwoko cen, ma tuko planet. Greenhouse pa Lobo obedo +33°C (gwoko kwo). Mega me Venus obedo +510°C (pe ki gwokke). Mars cok pe tye ki mo (-60°C i dye). Dit pa gas me greenhouse aye keto agikki!",
      "magnetic_shields": "Gwok me Magnet",
      "a_planet_s_magnetic_field_creates_a_ma": "Teko me magnet pa planet cweyo \"magnetosphere\" — gwok ma pe nen ma ryemo woko yamo me ceŋ (jami ma tye ki charge ma a ki i Ceŋ). Magnetosphere pa Lobo gwoko yamo megwa dok miyo kwo bedo. Mars orwenyo teko mere me magnet i mwaka bilion 4 mukato, ci giywayo yamo mere woko mot mot. Magnetosphere pa Jupiter tek tyen 20,000 loyo mega me Lobo!",
      "why_isn_t_pluto_a_planet": "Piŋo Pluto Pe Planet?",
      "in_2006_the_international_astronomical": "I 2006, International Astronomical Union oketo lok adek ma nyuto planet: (1) Wiro i kom Ceŋ ✓, (2) Tye ki pek ma romo miyo kite doko ryeŋryeŋ ✓, (3) \"Ojwayo yo mere me wir\" ki jami mukene ✗. Pluto rwate kabedo mere me wir ki jami alip mapol me Kuiper Belt, mumiyo gilwoŋe ni \"dwarf planet.\" Man pe miyo doko gin ma pe mit — New Horizons onyuto ni pud tye ka tic i kome!",
      "tidal_locking": "Tidal Locking",
      "over_billions_of_years_gravitational_t": "I kare pa bilion mwaka, teko me kwot pa gravity twero miyo wir pa dwe doko mot nio ka orwate ki kare mere me wir madit. Agikki: tuŋ acel nyuto i planet kare ducu. Dwe megwa gimake ki Lobo (tidally locked). Mercury gimake nucce ki Ceŋ (rate me 3:2). Pluto ki Charon gimako kekengi — ginyuto tuŋ acel-lu bot kekengi kare ducu!",
      "searching_for_life": "Yenyo kwo",
      "a_biosignature_is_any_evidence_of_past": "Biosignature obedo lanyut mo keken pa kwo macon onyo ma tye kombeddi. Lupwony yenyo: (1) pii ma mol, (2) organic molecule, (3) gas i yamo calo oxygen onyo methane ma pe romo bedo ka pe kwo aye cweyo, (4) ka ma teko a ki iye. Kabedo maber loyo i solar system megwa: Mars (pii macon), Europa (nam i te del), Enceladus (yamo pii ma tuc), ki Titan (nam me methane).",
