      "inquiry_widget_no_score_no_reveal_no_a": "Widget me nono — wel pe, nyuto lagam pe, cwalo lagam pe. T = √(a³/M) kit ma Kepler III waco, ki M i pek me ceŋ, a i AU, T i mwaka. Gitiyo ki Vis-viva pi v i perihelion / aphelion.",
