      "each_fuzzy_blob_is_a_galaxy_of_100_bil": "Nyig ma col acel acel obedo galaxy ma tye ki lakalatwe milion o wa i mia me bilion",
      "zoom": "Zoom",
      "in_1995_hubble_pointed_at_a_tiny_dark_": "I 1995, Hubble oneno kabedo matidi macol i polo pi nino 10. Agikki: galaxy 3000 ma bor i cal acel. JWST otero man tut loyo, ka kwano galaxy ma a ki i mia me milion mwaka mukwoŋo i ŋe Big Bang.",
      "star_color_temperature": "🌟 Rangi + Lyeto pa Lakalatwe",
