      "temperature": "Lyeto",
      "star_color_temperature_astronomy_mnemo": "Rangi pa lakalatwe = lyeto. Lok me poyo wic pa lupwony me lakalatwe pi OBAFGKM (ki ma lyet loyo o i ma ŋic loyo): 'Oh Be A Fine Girl/Guy, Kiss Me.' Lakalatwe ma lyet loyo dit loyo + ryeny loyo + kwo cek loyo.",
      "tidal_locking_simulator": "🔒 Simulator me Tidal Locking",
      "why_does_the_moon_always_show_the_same": "Piŋo Dwe nyuto tuŋ acel-lu kare ducu? Teko me kwot omiyo wir mere odoko mot. Nen kit ma bor + pek loko kare me mako kwede.",
      "planet_2": "Planet",
