      "spin_angle": "Angle pa wir",
      "axis_tilt": "Jengo pa yo me wir",
      "a_pulsar_is_a_rapidly_rotating_neutron": "Pulsar obedo neutron star ma wiro oyot twatwal. Tuŋ mere me magnet cwalo ryeny me radiation. Waneno mil keken ka ryeny okato i komwa — calo lamp me nam. Mukene mil tyen 700 i cekonde acel. Jocelyn Bell Burnell onoŋo mukwoŋo i 1967.",
      "solar_wind_streamer": "💨 Yamo me Ceŋ ma Mol",
      "stream_of_charged_particles_from_sun_h": "Mol pa jami ma tye ki charge ma a ki i Ceŋ, ma goyo Lobo. Yamo matek loyo = aurora mapol + peko i GPS.",
      "earth_13": "Lobo",
      "wind_speed": "Yot pa yamo",
      "density": "Dwoŋ",
      "solar_wind_is_a_stream_of_charged_part": "Yamo me ceŋ obedo mol pa jami ma tye ki charge (dwoŋ mere proton + electron) ma mol ki i Ceŋ kare ducu. Yot mere lokke i kin 250-800 km/s. Rumo matek kelo aurora + twero balo GPS + laŋo me mac. Gin ma otimme i Carrington i 1859: telegraph opyet ci owaŋ.",
      "iss_orbital_position": "🛰 Ka ma ISS Tye iye i Wir",
      "the_iss_orbits_earth_every_90_minutes_": "ISS wiro i kom Lobo i dakika 90 acel acel. Kare mukene tye i ceŋ, kare mukene tye i tipo pa Lobo.",
      "orbit_3": "Yo me wir",
      "the_iss_orbits_400_km_up_at_17_500_mph": "ISS wiro i bor pa km 400 i yot pa 17,500 mph (28,000 km/h). Tyeko wir acel i dakika 90 — mumiyo luwot me polo gineno wok pa ceŋ + poto pa ceŋ tyen 16 i nino acel. ISS obedo gin madit loyo ma dano gugedo i polo.",
      "voyager_position_tracker": "🚀 Lalub me Ka ma Voyager Tye iye",
      "voyager_1_2_launched_1977_they_are_now": "Voyager 1 + 2 gucwalogi i 1977. Kombeddi gitye i polo ma i kin lakalatwe; Voyager 1 okato heliopause i 2012 dok Voyager 2 i 2018.",
      "year": "Mwaka",
      "voyagers_1_2_launched_1977_to_study_ou": "Gucwalo Voyager 1 + 2 i 1977 me kwano planet ma woko. Gin aryo ducu gukato heliopause (aguu pa yamo me ceŋ) i 2012 + 2018 — kombeddi gitye i polo ma i kin lakalatwe. Acel acel tero Golden Record ki mot + wer pi jami mo keken ma nongogi.",
      "mercury_transit": "🌑 Kato pa Mercury",
      "mercury_passes_in_front_of_the_sun_eve": "Mercury kato i nyim Ceŋ i kin mwaka manok. Nen ka kato — ento ki solar filter maber keken.",
      "watch_with_proper_solar_filter_only_ne": "Nen ki solar filter MABER keken — PE inen tir ki waŋi!",
      "time_3": "Kare",
      "a_transit_happens_when_mercury_or_venu": "Kato timme ka Mercury (onyo Venus) kato i kin Lobo + Ceŋ. Nen calo waŋ macol matidi i kom Ceŋ. Kato pa Mercury ma bino: Nowembe 13, 2032. Kato pa Venus ma bino: Dicembe 2117 — pe bidwogo doki nio wa 2125.",
      "foucault_pendulum": "🎯 Pendulum pa Foucault",
      "l_on_foucault_1851_proved_earth_rotate": "Léon Foucault i 1851 onyuto ni Lobo wiro ki pendulum madit. Kit ma yeŋo iye lokke yot loyo i tuŋ malo ki piny.",
      "foucault_pendulum_2": "Pendulum pa Foucault",
      "latitude_3": "Latitude",
      "hours_elapsed": "Cawa ma okato",
      "l_on_foucault_1851_demonstrated_earth_": "Léon Foucault i 1851 onyuto wir pa Lobo ki pendulum madit. Kabedo ma yeŋo iye nen calo wiro pien Lobo wiro i te. I tuŋ malo ki piny: cawa 24. I dye kor lobo: matwal pe. I Maine: cawa ~34.",
      "saturn_hexagon": "⬡ Nget Abicel pa Saturn",
      "saturn_s_north_pole_has_a_perfect_hexa": "Tuŋ acam pa Saturn tye ki rumo ma tye ki nget abicel ma lac mere km 30,000. Voyager onoŋo i 1981.",
      "saturn_s_hexagonal_pole_storm": "Rumo me Nget Abicel i Tuŋ pa Saturn",
      "persistent_feature_30_000_km_wide_5_ea": "Gin ma pe rwenyo ma lac mere km 30,000 — kato tyen 2 loyo lac pa Lobo",
      "rotation": "Wir",
      "saturn_has_a_perfect_hexagonal_storm_a": "Saturn tye ki rumo ma nget abicel opore i tuŋ acam mere — Voyager aye ogamo cal mere mukwoŋo (1981), ci Cassini omoko ada. Nget abicel-li lac mere km 30,000 dok pe rwenyo. Piŋo nget abicel? Kit pa jet stream i yamo + Rossby wave.",
      "sundial_demo": "🕰 Nyuto pa Cawa me Ceŋ",
      "the_original_clock_as_the_sun_arcs_acr": "Cawa mukwoŋo. Macalo Ceŋ kato i polo, gnomon poyo tipo ma wiro ma nyuto cawa.",
      "hour": "Cawa",
      "sundials_predate_clocks_by_millennia_a": "Cawa me ceŋ obedo con loyo cawa me nyonyo pi mwaka alip mapol. Macalo Ceŋ wot i polo, tipo pa gnomon wiro. Jo Ejipt macon, Girik, Roma, ki Cayina ducu gugedo cawa me ceŋ ma opore. Mega me tin myero olok pi daylight saving time + equation of time.",
      "local_group_map": "🌐 Map me Local Group",
