      "eccentricity_2": "Eccentricity",
      "orbital_eccentricity_goes_from_0_perfe": "Eccentricity me yo me wir cakke ki 0 (ryeŋryeŋ ma opore) o i 1 (parabolic ma a woko). Planet cok ryeŋryeŋ. Comet cal ki toŋ twatwal — gicito cok ki Ceŋ + bor i kabedo ma woko. Yo me wir me hyperbolic (e>1) nyuto kato tyen acel keken i solar system.",
