      "earth_rotates_15_per_hour_utc_coordina": "Lobo wiro 15° i cawa acel acel. UTC (Coordinated Universal Time) obedo kare ma lobo ducu tiyo kwede. Kare pa kabedo mapatpat lokke ki ±cawa. Portland me Maine tye i UTC-5 (EST) onyo UTC-4 (EDT). I lobo ducu, nucce acel me Lobo tye i dyeceŋ ka nucce mukene tye i dyewor.",
