      "gas_giants_spin_fast_because_of_how_th": "Gas giant wiro oyot pi kit ma gicweyogi kwede. Venus wiro mot loyo, gwok pi kwot me ceŋ + yamo mere ma dwoŋ. Lobo dwoko mot ki ~milisecond 1.7 i mia me mwaka acel acel pi gravity pa Dwe.",
