      "best_naked_eye_observing_dark_site_awa": "Neno maber ki waŋ dano: kabedo macol (ka bor ki mac me gaŋ), Dwe i te aguu me neno, waŋi orwatte (dakika 20-30 i colpiny). App ma nono: Stellarium, SkyView, Star Walk konyo me ŋiyo gin ma ineno.",
      "pale_blue_dot": "🌍 Nyig Matidi ma Bulu",
