      "the_pale_blue_dot": "Nyig Matidi ma Bulu",
      "from_this_distant_vantage_point_the_ea": "\"Ki i kabedo man ma bor, Lobo twero nen calo pe tye ki pire mo. Ento bot wan, tye pat. Tam doki i kom nyig-gi. Mano en kany. Mano en gaŋwa. Mano en wan. I komme dano ducu ma imaro, dano ducu ma iŋeyo, dano ducu ma dong iwinyo pi kome, dano ducu ma gubedo, gukwo kwo gi.\"",
      "carl_sagan_pale_blue_dot_1994": "— Carl Sagan, Pale Blue Dot (1994)",
      "voyager_1_took_this_photo_of_earth_fro": "Voyager 1 ogamo cal man pa Lobo ki i bor pa bilion km 6 i Feb 14, 1990 — Carl Sagan aye okwayo. Lobo obedo pixel acel. Dano ducu ma gukwo i lobo gubedo i pixel-li.",
      "famous_nebulae": "☁ Nebula ma Gingeyo",
