      "drive_30_min_from_city_lights_maine_is": "Kwat dakika 30+ ka bor ki mac me gaŋ. Maine opoŋ ki gin magi. Katahdin Woods and Waters obedo kabedo ma gimoko ni polo mere col.",
      "most_important_tool_dark_sky_light_pol": "Gin ma pire tek loyo: polo macol. Mac ma pol tyeko lakalatwe 90%. Katahdin Woods and Waters NM ki AMC Maine Woods gin kabedo me International Dark Sky ma gimoko; Acadia ki Baxter bene gitye ki polo macol maber twatwal.",
