      "how_a_star_dies_depends_almost_entirel": "Kit ma lakalatwe to kwede jenge dwoŋ mere i pek mere ma ocakke kwede. Aguu ma tye i kin neutron star + black hole pe gimoko ada (aguu me Tolman-Oppenheimer-Volkoff ~2-3 M☉ pi gin ma odoŋ).",
      "cosmic_distance_reference": "📏 Lok me Bor i Polo",
