      "distances_jump_in_scale_km_to_au_to_ly": "Bor kato oyot i rom: km o i AU o i ly o i bilion me ly. Kit acel acel dit tyen ~10,000-100,000. Astronomy kwo i rom me log.",
      "maine_night_sky_by_season": "🌲 Polo me Dyewor i Maine i Kare acel acel",
      "maine_has_world_class_dark_skies_what_": "Maine tye ki polo macol maber twatwal i lobo ducu. Gin ma myero iyeny i kare acel acel.",
      "maine_has_fantastic_dark_skies_especia": "Maine tye ki polo macol maber twatwal — loyo ka i tuŋ acam me gaŋi madongo. Katahdin Woods and Waters NM ki AMC Maine Woods gin kabedo me International Dark Sky ma gimoko; Acadia, Allagash, Baxter, ki Cobscook bene col maber. Dyewor me kare me koyo bor + leŋ twatwal.",
      "space_news_timeline": "📰 Kare me Lok me Polo",
